SELF_ATTENDEE_STATUS

static final String SELF_ATTENDEE_STATUS
This is a copy of the attendee status for the owner of this event. This field is copied here so that we can efficiently filter out events that are declined without having to look in the Attendees table.

Type: INTEGER (int)
